 This project demonstrates the use of Restful JAX-RS.
To build the project use:
	mvn clean package
To run the project in tomcat, install the war file from the
target folder as ecommerce.war to the webapps folder of the
tomcat installation.
Make sure you rename the war file.

Restart the tomcat server and then visit the URL

http://localhost:8080/ecommerce/myapp/customers/all